{"tid":2124891,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Gan充電 + usb c 轉magsafe2 線 + mac air 2015得唔得？","createTime":"2020-07-25T18:20:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T15:10:22.000Z","uid":153938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"23a18a675aa28380bf7c1ffb5d88e3589b5378a8","tid":2124891,"uid":153938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T18:20:55.000Z","msg":"舊charger 條線爆哂，買新嘅差唔多6舊水，<br />\n但用嚟買<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">Gan充電頭</span></span>就細啲仲可以叉哂其他電子產品。<br />\n<br />\n問題重點係， <span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"blue\">usb type-c 轉 magsafe2 線</span></span>究竟可唔可靠？<br />\n如果唔係用OEM充電器，部macbook係咪讀唔到個充電頭 id，會唔會出事？<br />\n<br />\n如果有巴絲打用過/推介嘅請分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7e891b81cf0de5ffa1015cbebb1832110e53c98","tid":2124891,"uid":153938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T18:21:19.000Z","msg":"求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3a8ca4a0eba5e3a6084f543140ed6040932d2b","tid":2124891,"uid":153938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T18:24:19.000Z","msg":"求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad669dac5000b8cff8dcdc80c5af4980fc17867","tid":2124891,"uid":3675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T18:36:21.000Z","msg":"1. UsbC 轉magsafe 依種non standard 玩法 唔好update個os 有可能更新會失效 <br />\n好多假Apple Watch線都係更新會失效<br />\n<br />\n2. Gan仲好新 你話充不同產品 假設你起碼買2c1a<br />\n第一代gan 2c1a會炒車 兩件pd產品叫changer 比唔同電壓 結果充到斷下斷下 係咁閃mon <br />\n選擇方面要花功夫"},{"pid":"4612d49cbe6e4a33829421a547f791ae80dc5efe","tid":2124891,"uid":153938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ad669da